  "body": "<figure>\n\n\n<img src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595913830778-JJGPOL2JKMDUXC3318SZ/image-asset.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n</figure>\n\n\n\n\n\n<img alt=\"7b-IMG_9333.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595913860555-NQBFBLANMCOXS5DDJJWW/7b-IMG_9333.jpeg\">\n</img>\n\n<img alt=\"7e-IMG_9342.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595913881053-NGXIWBB32F2YRW1YS7WX/7e-IMG_9342.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7c-IMG_9334.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595913860959-1X5XRLM92U86DIR7TMJ8/7c-IMG_9334.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7f-IMG_9348.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595913880768-1M6AB4BPCUZ20I7MJKXL/7f-IMG_9348.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7g-travnotebook.jpg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595913881891-NXECSF0ZCMO5VXZ09COW/7g-travnotebook.jpg\"/>\n\n\n<img alt=\"7d-IMG_9336.jpeg\" src=\"https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5dd0ae59b4b4b35c07faf907/1595913861623-TQB6MMYX7H5LWUEIIU11/7d-IMG_9336.jpeg\"/>\n\n\n\n\n<p>photos by <a href=\"http://annmarieloves.com/\">Ann-Marie Espinoza</a></p><p>Ahh - the custom stamps I designed exclusively for <a href=\"http://www.papertales.com/store/p20/Amy_Tan_%26_Paper_Tales_Photopolymer_Stamp.html\">Paper Tales in San Diego</a> are back in stock. After tons of phone requests, they have made them available online <a href=\"http://www.papertales.com/store/p20/Amy_Tan_%26_Paper_Tales_Photopolymer_Stamp.html\">here</a>. Also it seems that my latest collection with American Crafts has been restocked in a lot of places. Find Better Together at <a href=\"http://goo.gl/DCUYhD\">scrapbook.com</a> and <a href=\"http://goo.gl/h4JNsN\">Simon Says Stamp</a>.</p>"
